casebody.data:
FEDERAL NATIONAL MORTGAGE ASSOCIATION, petitioner,
v.
Loraine SUNDQUIST. No. 13-852. Supreme Court of the United States Nov. 10, 2014.

Opinion

Motion of The Clearing House Association L.L.C. for leave to file a brief as amicus curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Utah denied.
